// • Section 6 (TP/Exit qty + % + triggers) -> 20a Sizing, 21a TP Engine, 21b Override Exits, 21c Standard TP Execution.
// • Section 7 (SL + MAE + risk caps) -> 20b Entry validation (MAE dual-cap), 21d Stop/Exit Orders.
// • Section 8 (Break Even inputs) -> 21 Exit Management (BE manager).
// • Section 9 (Trail inputs) -> 21 Exit Management (trail lock/advance + SL tightening).
// • Section 10 (Safety/ATR filter) -> 19 Arming gates, 20b Entry allowance.
// • Section 11 (daily/session/killzone) -> 18 Compliance gates, 21e Compliance Closes.
